BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p> Let&#x27\;s do it again! Wilma will have a picnic with you on the Isar! </p><p>We&#x27\;ll  play outdoor games\, snack on fruit\, chat a lot or just relax and enjoy  the sun.<br/>If you have a picnic blanket\, bring it along! Please also  remember to bring enough water and sun protection. And if you can\, you  are also welcome to bring snacks for the picnic.<br/>The meeting point is the diversity Jugendzentrum\, Blumenstr. 11. At 19:15 we will go to the Isar together\, so if you would like to join us later\, please write to us via the contact form.<br/>If it rains\, we&#x27\;ll have an indoor picnic in the café (Blumenstraße 29)\, so bring your blanket anyway!<br/>Wilma are looking forward to a sunny and fun picnic with you! </p>
DTEND:20250815T200000Z
DTSTART:20250815T170000Z
SUMMARY:Wilmas gehen an die Isar
UID:c2304736-550e-4bbe-ab01-0c2ad8d33ca8@c230.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p> </p><p>Do you paint\, write\, knit\, or engage in other creative activities? Then come to Wilma&#x27\;s creative evening! Bring along the project you are currently working on or a new project and look forward to crafting together.</p><p>If you don&#x27\;t have your own project at the moment\, you can also make bracelets using materials from diversity. </p><p>The Wilmas look forward to a creative-chatty-colourful evening with you!</p>
DTEND:20250904T200000Z
LOCATION:diversity Jugendzentrum\, Blumenstraße 11\, 80331\, München
DTSTART:20250904T170000Z
SUMMARY:Wilma - Kreativabend
